# Testimonial Images

Drop customer photos here. Name them to match the `image` field in `src/data/testimonials.js`.

Example:
  priya-sharma.jpg
  rajesh-nair.jpg
  sunita-verma.jpg
  ...

Supported formats: jpg, jpeg, png, webp
Recommended size: 200×200 px minimum, square crop

Images are served at: /testimonials/<filename>
